{"tid":1454864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日再去機場","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:09:19.000Z","uid":77089,"like":49,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bbe16d53f447fd24c250a0bf15ad022a74f720","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"同意請正<br />\n不同意請負皮<br />\n終於癱瘓機場 令全世界都知香港出事<br />\n但一日真係唔夠"},{"pid":"9c65a3daefece873fd084f463998d692f1b0bdbe","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"兩日都chur?"},{"pid":"82da5255c8d72fd2138429d90d17299321dbd151","tid":1454864,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:27:12.000Z","msg":"出面世界知，但你地拎唔到去機場班市民民心呢"},{"pid":"c7a511db24e8bdda9f3dc78b85142fc131f59767","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"定係要一連兩日先夠力?"},{"pid":"b21359604ade45aabb32f48238f4b8413bafeaca","tid":1454864,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有航班已取消!<br />\n機場圍捕無路走！<br />\n所有手足請即散<br />\n記得係一齊散<br />\n唔好落單！<br />\n擇日再戰<br />\n切實執行不被捕原則！<br />\n仲有咩好留呀 叫你留個d 自己諗下係咪鬼啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYyt3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYyt3j.png&h=916dd304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMoRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMoRgG.png&h=734c1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBrP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBrP8.png&h=f9aef586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8edd67c4aa54bc1e1f46662ecabe8bb78ab7f702","tid":1454864,"uid":72737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"轉<br />\n<br />\nT1有咩事記住去T2<br />\n<br />\n*去T2方法*:<br />\n- 係離境嗰層，行去機鐵個位，有escalator落一層就係T2<br />\n- 去到T2上一層有好多餐廳、food court，有戲院！<br />\n- 去到T2，如落一層就係停車場<br />\n<br />\n*去富豪酒店 Regal Airport Hotel方法*:<br />\n- Arrival Hall A 有條行人天橋，只有一條路，行過去就係<br />\n- 現時只有Regal正門可以合法上的士、Uber (不過今日唔知啲車入唔入到)<br />\n<br />\n*去國泰城方法* :<br />\n- Arrival Hall 任何一條樓梯落去 (有防煙門嗰啲) 就到巴士站嗰層，有幾個shuttle係去CXCity and KA House/ 民航處"},{"pid":"65fca7f5114738bf76a265207d7a2cad80ebe261","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:33:41.000Z","msg":"【社區革命】今晚起請堅持每晚十點，所有人一齊向窗口嗌出你既憤怒，向世界吶喊出香港人既呼聲。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454498</a>"},{"pid":"2ea0256aeda1f1561ab91598fb879f0ce6566faf","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02d70cbe58ff872f46c49a141e612a2a6cc0e491","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:46:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f568f3d3b94006e62fca9fa24b33392789129070","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"571583c78e3622aeed5bbb07cd623a921601016e","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7669afa288dcb8873911d52cda76fb8edaf1e8f8","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"聽日我會去 希望有人一齊去"},{"pid":"53b4ab002141b18acd9b96b9d765db2953959d28","tid":1454864,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊去"},{"pid":"dc4e840fc723ae99d98739c493038710c643bb88","tid":1454864,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呢類POST要蓋過所有守留 POST"},{"pid":"0211a1e882dfd1a17eaafc5cb34c37535f3274af","tid":1454